Class EfficientPriorityQueue<T>

  • java.lang.Object

          • org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.util.EfficientPriorityQueue<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, Queue<T>
    public class EfficientPriorityQueue<T>
extends PriorityQueue<T>
    Extends PriorityQueue with an efficient contains method that avoids to loop through the queue to find an element. Instead it checks if the elements hash code is stored in a separate HashSet.
